data.description: Fiesta offers miles of nature paths, several parks and that community feel you're looking for!You will enjoy coming home to this adorable open concept home nestled in the heart of the community and just five minutes from shopping, restaurants, and schools.  This Clayton plan has 9ft ceilings and large windows brighten this incredible space!  The huge kitchen and large kitchen island provide ample storage and prep space.  With three spacious bedrooms, this home will provide plenty of space!
